data.job_description:
An established energy client of mine is looking for an experienced Web Developer to join their team on an initial 6-month contract. Starting 6/5, you will be working in an agile team to help develop a new set of web applications for their own system and sub vendors. This role is hybrid hybrid and you will be required to go in to the office 3 days p/w.

Full-Stack Web Developer

6-month contract (likely extension)

Houston - Hybrid working

W2 - $70 - $75 p/h

C2C - $80 - $90 p/h

Starting 06/05

Technical requirements;

JavaScript, (React OR Angular OR Vue), Node, HTML, CSSS, API

(NO EMPLOYERS OR RECRUTIERS)

Oscar Associates Limited (US) is acting as an Employment Business in relation to this vacancy.

Web Developer - 6-month Contract - Hybrid
